      <byline class="print_byline">By HOWARD W. FRENCH</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">French, Howard W</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>China's government, in effort to conserve energy, urges office workers to abandon business suits in favor of T-shirts and other informal wear; air-conditioning in many government offices has been turned off and inspectors sent to hotels and office buildings in Beijing to enforce new temperature guidelines (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>In an effort to conserve energy, the government has urged office workers to abandon business suits in favor of T-shirts and other informal wear. The message was delivered in a week when air-conditioning in many government offices was turned off and inspectors sent to hotels and office buildings in Beijing to enforce new temperature guidelines.</p>
        <p>HOWARD W. FRENCH</p>
